data.description: Horse property. Large plot for the area at 10 acres. Beautiful views. Mature Russian olive trees, and lilac bushes. Three sheds for plenty of storage.
data.whatILove: One of the bedrooms is set up as an office. There are two master suites. There are two beautiful private yards with decks. The rest of the lands is two pastures. Fire pit in larger back yard. Horses Stalls and pasture. Plenty of parking and space. Very large wood stove.
